-- lib.card-description: GAS FEE CREDITS
note: The campaign plan purchase does NOT include gas fees credit by default. Purchase is optional. 
description: To minimize frequent use of credit card multiple times per campaign, it is however recommended to avail & allocate sufficient gas fee credits accordingly.

Every transaction that happens over a blockchain (minting NFTs / transferring
NFTs etc.) invoke **gas fees**.  The actual cost incurred depend on  multiple
factors and varies from chain to chain. Basic principles of supply & demand
impacts its value in real-time.

